She could have made candy,

16
00:02:17,630 --> 00:02:20,730
or fireworks,
or sparkly underwear...

17
00:02:20,730 --> 00:02:26,050
for wrestlers,
but no, she chose shoes.

18
00:02:28,610 --> 00:02:30,920
Then she taught her daughter
to make shoes.

19
00:02:32,310 --> 00:02:34,890
And later,
she taught her son-in-law.

20
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:37,880
Then her grandkids
got roped in.

21
