He wants no part
of your music, mariachi.

134
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:16,250
You keep away from him.

135
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:23,690
Ay, pobrecito.
Oh, estas bien, mijo.

136
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:27,930
You know better than to
be here in this place!

137
00:08:27,930 --> 00:08:31,320
You will come home. Now.

138
00:08:41,350 --> 00:08:42,980
How many times
have we told you?

139
00:08:42,980 --> 00:08:45,350
That plaza is
crawling with mariachis.

140
00:08:45,350 --> 00:08:47,590
Yes, Tio Berto.

141
00:08:47,590 --> 00:08:50,720
- No, no, no, no, no!
- Ah! Go away, you. Go!

142
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:51,990
It's just Dante.

143
00:08:51,990 --> 00:08:54,120
Never name a street dog.

144
00:08:54,130 --> 00:08:57,180
They'll follow you forever.
Now, go get my shoe.

145
00:09:03,300 --> 00:09:06,040
I found your son
in Mariachi Plaza.

146
00:09:06,040 --> 00:09:07,100
Ay, Miguel!

147
00:09:07,110 --> 00:09:09,740
You know how Abuelita
feels about the plaza.

148
00:09:09,740 --> 00:09:11,040
