because I care, Miguel.

189
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:03,300
Miguel? Miguel?

190
00:11:06,260 --> 00:11:09,390
What are we going
to do with that boy?

191
00:11:09,390 --> 00:11:13,450
You're right.
That's just what he needs.

192
00:11:37,390 --> 00:11:39,120
It's you. Get in here.

193
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:42,190
Come on, Dante. Hurry up!

194
00:11:42,190 --> 00:11:44,160
You're gonna
get me in trouble, boy.

195
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:45,750
Someone could hear me.

196
00:11:50,470 --> 00:11:52,440
I wish someone
wanted to hear me.

197
00:11:53,770 --> 00:11:56,760
Other than you. Ew. Okay.

198
00:11:58,340 --> 00:12:00,490
Perfecto!

199
00:12:33,910 --> 00:12:36,480
I have to sing.
I have to play!

200
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:41,230
The music, it's not
just in me, it is me.

201
00:12:43,020 --> 00:12:46,140
When life gets me down,
I play my guitar.

202
00:12:47,060 --> 00:12:49,260
The rest of the world
may follow the rules,

203
00:12:49,260 --> 00:12:52,140
but I must follow my heart.

204
00:12:52,530 --> 00:12:54,200
Ugh!

205
