246
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:12,140
You'll be making them
every day after school.

247
00:15:12,140 --> 00:15:15,210
Oh! Our Migueli-ti-ti-ti-to

248
00:15:15,210 --> 00:15:17,670
carrying on
the family tradition.

